語用學專題研究                           SEMINAR ON PRAGMATICS


  	In this course, we will discuss the following topics: sense and reference, speech act theory, indirect language, cooperative principle and neo-griceanism, relevance theory, pragmatic studies of politeness and presupposition.In this course, we will study the interaction between language and contexts, i.e. how contexts affect linguistic meaning. We focus on language use in contexts and the meanings of utterances for communication. Three groups of topics will be covered in this semester: Common topics in pragmatics, pragmatics and discourse, pragmatics and its interfaces. In this semester, it will cover the following subtopics: language and language use (WK1-3), face theory & politeness (WK4-6), conversational implicature (WK7-9), speech act (WK10), and metaphor (WK15-17).
In this course, we will study the interaction between language and contexts, i.e. how contexts affect linguistic meaning. We focus on language use in contexts and the meanings of utterances for communication. Three groups of topics will be covered in this semester: Common topics in pragmatics, pragmatics and discourse, pragmatics and its interfaces. In this semester, it will cover the following subtopics: language and language use (WK1-3), face theory & politeness (WK4-6), conversational implicature (WK7-9), speech act (WK10), and metaphor (WK15-17).

課程教育目標 

A 強化外國文學、文化、語言學理論與知識 To enable students to improve their knowledge and theory in the fields of foreign literatures, cultures and linguisticsB 培育外國文學及語言學領域的專業教學與學術研究人才 To cultivate talented people specializing in teaching and research in the disciplines of foreign literatures and linguisticsC 訓練學生進行研究、撰寫學術論文的能力 To enable students to develop their capabilities for research and academic writingD 培養獨立整合及創意思考的能力，發展專業且獨特研究觀點 To enable students to cultivate their capabilities for independent integration and creativie thinking and  develop their professionalism and unique research perspectives 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

B 獨立思考、思辨、反省與推己及人

E 熟稔各種理論基礎、收集分析文獻資料的能力

F 完成學術論文及批判性書寫的能力

G 深入閱讀並解析外國文學、語言、文化等作品與論文的能力

H 國際視野、跨領域研究及適應能力


